Geithner Says U.S. Has ‘Huge Stake’ in Europe Resolving Crisis

-- B y   H a n s   N i c h o l s
-- 
2011-09-19T15:59:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/geithner-says-u-s-has-huge-stake-in-europe-resolving-crisis.html
U.S. Treasury Secretary  Timothy
Geithner  said the U.S. has a “huge stake” in  Europe ’s efforts
to resolve its debt crisis and is “working very closely” with
the continent’s leaders and “being very supportive.”  “It’s not a question of the financial resources, the
economic resources of that great continent,” Geithner told
reporters at a White House briefing. “This is within their
means to resolve.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Hans Nichols in Washington at 
 hnichols2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Drummond at 
 bdrummond@bloomberg.net  